World Tree
RECOMMENDED LEVEL: 15-20
Anyone who's made it this far must be bright
enough to get through the Lost Forest's maze-like
structure. However, any smart adventurer would
end their journey right here and retrace their steps.
The World Tree has stood at this very spot in
Telluria Field for as long as anyone can remember.
It's been growing for millenia upon millenia, and
doesn't show any signs of stopping.
Rumor has is it that a very powerful foe
resides at the peak of the tree... which
is the reason that the best advice that
can be given is to run away, now.
But if one really wishes to brave the World Tree...
Please have proper adventuring gear
before entering!
Going further in unprepared may very well be the
end of you! Proceed with caution!
